snippet.title: Pasha Pasha 2 arcade 3 player Netplay
snippet.description:
I'm player 1, Mark is player 2 and MrMario is player 3. Note that this game only runs at 30fps. There was a problem with the graphics on the penguin minigame, but in the minigame selection, I switched emulators to get the correct graphics. I think this game is supposed to have music, but it's not emulated at this time.
@MrMariobros222
